{
  "stem": "13457.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so, now I can come to, now I can come to, to the end of this chapter, out of [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] out of Warsaw, the German beginning of it, into Russia, and the next two years in Russia until the breakout of '41 war.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I will stop here, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I think the tape is ending here now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have few more minutes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, now, so-- so then we come to my aunt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And already, my other aunt with her two children is there, Kraushar, with her two boys and her husband, also a physician.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And initially, all these three sisters with a whole bunch of kids are in-- were in one apartment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Within few months, also my uncle, Shimon, from the-- my father's side came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Jerrzyk, my cousin from my paternal uncle, Daniel, came there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Also Wladek came, the son of my maternal sister, Basia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And now all these people came because they were young, and they could walk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they walked, whatever it took, to cross the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and the whole mishpokhe was in one place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I went to school, to Russian school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I learned Russian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my father was working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And nobody lived in one-- in complete peace of mind these two years preceding the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Actually, it's a year and a half or so, where anxiety the Germans were still-- may still go farther.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was worry number one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the main worry was that the Russians were deport all these people that crossed the border into Siberia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And several members of our family were deported into Siberia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was discussed, should we go inside Russia, deportation or otherwise, or should we say in eastern Poland and risk the second appearance of, of Germans?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's it?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
